Detailed Description

This class holds information about the Nodes that this tracker affects and the weightings for each node and the limits of yaw and pitch.

void ArmTrackerNodeInfo::getTrackedDirection ( Vector3 &  direction  )  [virtual]

This method accepts a direction vector and updates it to the current direction of the manipulated bipeds.

In the case of the ArmTracker we need to directions so set these in the lookAt function

Parameters:
direction This vector is the result of the calculation.
